require(flextable)
model='knowledge =~ general+symptoms+treatmt
empathy =~ cognitiv+emotion+disposit+attitude
intervention =~ classrm+instruct
intervention ~ b*empathy + c*knowledge
empathy ~ a*knowledge
indirect effect:=a*b
total effect:=c+(a*b)'
fit=sem(model,data=ADHD)
